{"tid":844912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：80000人次...已經唔存在喇","createTime":"2018-10-02T08:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T03:58:37.000Z","uid":4942,"like":312,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"5a3f1a2abd880321d0dba783f8fee7556bf14496","tid":844912,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:49:52.000Z","msg":"林鄭：高鐵日均8萬人次非目標是最佳估算　市民需適應一地兩檢<br />\n<br />\n廣深港高鐵香港段開通一星期多，均未能達致政府預期的每日8萬人次，<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭今出席行會前表示，8萬人次非目標而是最佳估算，期望能超過該數字</span>。她又稱「一地兩檢」是新事件，旅客和市民需時間適應，而昨日亦錄得7.8萬出入境人次。她相信高鐵和西九龍站有巨大前景，隨西九文化區開放將會吸引更多市民和旅客，不擔心其財政狀況。"},{"pid":"1dc6f3f5b048808c345629faec4719d034b9c04a","tid":844912,"uid":79563,"like":99,"dislike":5,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:50:35.000Z","msg":"即係任UP啦"},{"pid":"62e891f2ee6aeaf0bfbdd6b6e186625e20203f5a","tid":844912,"uid":95,"like":371,"dislike":4,"score":367,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:51:35.000Z","msg":"有幾多人搭都無所謂，反正錢又俾左，地又割埋。就算係零人次都唔會剷平個鳩鐵站！"},{"pid":"d1ee1654d7abc17ff4611b085cd6be08d92abc84","tid":844912,"uid":78533,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"唔撚係目標係咪即係一開始就打算送錢比狗鐵呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df9d80260ff491df6e0326b29846af0479f5265","tid":844912,"uid":35930,"like":41,"dislike":4,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:52:52.000Z","msg":"董伯伯個八幻五<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a21bd8bcf0d248c4cfa2f617a3219e1a0f5d70f","tid":844912,"uid":62226,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:54:34.000Z","msg":"唔起都起咗，除非拆咗個站，唔係嘅話最好就少啲人搭"},{"pid":"8cb69275d3108d1018b638d1b16def5e44753e8c","tid":844912,"uid":67876,"like":115,"dislike":2,"score":113,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:54:43.000Z","msg":"個龍門就快同對面個隊疊埋一舊<br />\n成場波就唔洗踢啦<img src=\"/a